# 1. Do you type on a desktop or laptop keyboard every day?

Yes, absolutely. As a computer science student, I spend a huge amount of time typing every single day, mostly on my laptop keyboard. I use it for coding, writing reports, taking notes and sometimes even chatting with classmates about projects. Since I often study in libraries or classrooms, a laptop is simply more convenient than a desktop. I’d say typing has become such a natural part of my daily routine that I barely notice how many hours I spend doing it.

### 中文翻译：

是的，当然。作为一名计算机专业的学生，我每天都要花很多时间打字，主要是在笔记本电脑键盘上。我会用它来写代码、完成报告、记笔记，有时候也会和同学讨论项目。因为我经常在图书馆或者教室学习，所以笔记本电脑比台式机更方便。我觉得打字已经成为我日常生活中非常自然的一部分了，甚至我都意识不到自己每天打了多少字。

---

# 2. When did you learn how to type on a keyboard?

I first learned how to type when I was in primary school, probably around the age of ten. At the beginning, I typed very slowly because I had to look at every single key. Later, when I became more interested in computers and programming during middle school, my typing speed improved naturally through constant practice. I didn’t really take formal typing lessons, but coding and gaming helped me become much faster and more accurate over time.

### 中文翻译：

我第一次学习键盘打字是在小学的时候，大概十岁左右。一开始我打字非常慢，因为我必须盯着每一个按键看。后来到了初中，我开始对电脑和编程产生兴趣，于是通过不断练习，我的打字速度自然提高了。我并没有专门上过正式的打字课程，不过编程和打游戏确实让我后来打字越来越快，也更准确。

---

# 3. How do you improve your typing?

I think the best way to improve typing is simply to practice consistently. Since I code quite often, I naturally type a lot every day, which helps build muscle memory. Besides that, I sometimes use typing websites to test my speed and accuracy, especially when I want to challenge myself. Another thing I pay attention to is typing without looking at the keyboard, because touch typing can significantly improve efficiency. Over time, I’ve noticed that my typing has become both faster and more comfortable.

### 中文翻译：

我觉得提高打字能力最好的方式就是持续练习。因为我经常写代码，所以每天都会自然地打很多字，这能帮助形成肌肉记忆。除此之外，我有时候也会用一些打字网站测试自己的速度和准确率，尤其是在我想挑战自己的时候。还有一点我会特别注意，就是尽量不低头看键盘，因为盲打能够明显提升效率。久而久之，我发现自己的打字不仅更快了，也更加轻松自然了。
